Encountered Shiny Errors

Published

January 7, 2022

Error Message :

Error in func(fname, ...) : app.R did not return a shiny.appobj object.

Cause : Curly bracket is missing.

Example : server <- function(input, output)

Solution : server <- function(input, output) {}
